Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all your idea to start with, Fuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut up, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you had a reason! This is going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{chi}Oh right, Mayaka, would you like some cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}At least pick up the damn phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}You can back out if you have to, just give me a call or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{chi}Uh... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}You {\i1}do{\i0} have a phone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{chi}Should I go get some milk, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}If it were just me then I wouldn't really care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}Don't make that face! Just listen to me, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}Don't you get the big picture here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{ho}A reckless person... Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}Just apologizing to me isn't gonna make this right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}It's ridiculous that someone so smart lacks the most basic consideration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{ho}You can't do a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}You knew what was going to happen, and still you said nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}It was raining, and windy, and it even started to hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}I bet you wouldn't have noticed even if you showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}but I actually bothered to pick some clothes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}and then I got soaked! Soaked! Do you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ma}And this is all {\i1}whose{\i0} fault? Guess who! It's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aren't you tired yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At least stop to breathe in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't do that for {\i0}your{\i1} sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you sure know how to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you relieve your stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you showed a little consideration I wouldn't get stressed to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you should take lessons from Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even seen her get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I've never seen you or Oreki get angry either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku does get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi can get really angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do it as enthusiastically as Mayaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but sometimes I blow my top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really imagine you actually getting angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only human, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He just acts all uppity and tries to hide his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he gets mad, he's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking me lightly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be... interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can totally imagine Chitanda coming up with some scheme to make Satoshi angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I expect great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get angry too, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki? Angry? No way in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's a nice guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's so pitifully dull that he can't even summon the energy to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, isn't that a bit too harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I got angry at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Houtarou's lack of emotions aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda's on a totally different level when it comes to not getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's just a matter of tolerance, but you should try to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,more calm, just like Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never be as calm as Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You're not praising me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say we kind of are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just making observations. It's not a matter of "good" or "bad".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, as long as it's not because you {\i1}can't{\i0} get angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,being able to stay calm is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger is a grave sin.{title ref}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You should treat me better than that, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the seven deadly sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Nice one, Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty famous, so I bet you've heard about them too, right, Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that much at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't there 108 sins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of worldly desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger, pride, gluttony, greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Envy, lust and sloth{ and 8thSin}{w}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sloth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What're you looking at {\i0}me{\i1} for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you're perfect, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard-working, you don't eat much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine you being greedy, and you're very diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not... lewd, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you show no signs of envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're not praising her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more like they're making fun of how perfect she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, sometimes when I get hungry I eat a whole lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, envy doesn't fit her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time we welcomed Saint Eru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name even sounds like an angel's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uriel, Gabriel, Chitanda Eriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She got angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She told us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, now you've gone and made her mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were totally into it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that people should never get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That applies to the other deadly sins as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I think that pride and greed are also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone didn't have any pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't they also be lacking in self-confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone was free of greed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't they have trouble supporting their family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And if people didn't envy one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't they stop inventing new things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You don't have to pay such close attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moderation in all things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the concept of "deadly sins" can be applied to our lives that simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think that getting angry isn't a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you say that if you can't get angry about anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really love anything either?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, how come you don't get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather save my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi-Chitanda's been infected by Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,An evil spirit is haunting Kamiyama High!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's known only as... "the low-energy lifestyle"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, please come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feel free to shut up any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kidding, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And here I thought I'd found my soulmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was a spur-of-the-moment thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I never get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I get angry if I see people wasting food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Each grain of rice is a drop of sweat!{proverb}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's from a family of farmers all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of getting angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't you the one who got angry in Omichi's class during fifth period?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I even forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to ask you about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't stop thinking... Can't stop thinking...{loop}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to ask you about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,During my fifth period math class,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I got angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand what made me get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That almost never happens to me at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so something must have set me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't stop thinking about it!
