Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had math class during fifth period today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Omichi is the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki and Fukube know what kind of a person he is, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll explain from the beginning anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He arrived to class right when the bell rung.
