Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to check the sign outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the first time he's done that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, he wrote a quadratic equation on the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The equation was quite simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.74,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\blur1.2\1a&H30&\fnpencilPete FONT\b1\c&HBCCAC1&\frz12.09\pos(954,544)}Range
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but the range of {\i1}x{\i0} was restricted.
